videos.description: Ebuka Izundu gets the second-chance bucket downlow for Miami.
videos.headline: Izundu stays with the play and gets the bucket

videos.description: Kyle Guy knocks down the wing 3-pointer for the Cavaliers.
videos.headline: Guy buries 2nd triple of the half for UVA

videos.description: Miami's Ebuka Izundu stays with the play once again and cleans with a huge slam.
videos.headline: Izundu cleans up with a big dunk after block

videos.description: Ebuka Izundu gets a bucket in traffic off a great look from Anthony Lawrence.
videos.headline: Izundu sparking 2nd-half run for Miami

videos.description: Lonnie Walker comes up with the steal and finishes with a pretty move in transition.
videos.headline: Walker snags the turnover chain for Miami

videos.description: Chris Lykes puts his defender on skates and then knocks down the 3-pointer for Miami.
videos.headline: Lykes breaks ankles and buries 3-pointer

videos.description: Kyle Guy starts to take over for UVA with a great move inside the paint.
videos.headline: Guy takes contact and gets the floater to go for UVA

videos.description: Virginia's De'Andre Hunter brings the hammer, dunking on Ebuka Izundu in the second half.
videos.headline: Hunter throws down vicious dunk against Miami

videos.description: Kyle Guy breaks down how Virginia handling playing as the No. 1 team in the nation and the performance of freshman De'Andre Hunter.
videos.headline: Guy: 'We had a lot of lows and a lot of highs tonight'
